     H            Y.
     F** FBCR83S******************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : SAVE FBCWP83(SALES-UP) TO FBCWP83S             *
     F*  WRITTEN    : 2023.09.21                                     *
     F*  WRITTEN BY : JW (SRA)                                       *
     *  ATTENTION  : COMPILE WITH OPTION - ALLOW NULL VALUES *YES   *
     F*             : -------------------------------                *
     F****************************************************************
     FFBCWP83 IF  E                    DISK
     FFBCWP83SO   E           K        DISK
      *---------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      ******************************************************
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      ******************************************************
     C                     TIME           SDATE
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ FBCWP83                  80
     C   80                LEAVE
      *
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     F8CRHZ
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       F8CRTM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     F8CRUS
     C                     MOVEL#PGM      F8CRPG
     C                     WRITEFBCWP83R
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
